            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7950,
            "LocalizeKR": "냐, 냐하하……\n저기~ 요~ 선생님~?",
            "LocalizeJP": "にゃ、にゃはは……\nもしも～し、先生～？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20046,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2004601,
            "DisplayOrder": 550,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 13880,
            "LocalizeKR": "어머어머, 무서운 얼굴…….\n선생님께 안 어울린답니다?",
            "LocalizeJP": "あらあら、怖い顔……。\n先生には似合いませんよぉ？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20046,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2004601,
            "DisplayOrder": 560,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7380,
            "LocalizeKR": "혹시나……\n정말로 화나셨나요~?",
            "LocalizeJP": "もしかして……\n本当に怒ってます？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20046,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2004601,
            "DisplayOrder": 570,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 13450,
            "LocalizeKR": "아니, 뭐, 알고는\n있습니다만, 아핫…….",
            "LocalizeJP": "いや、まぁ……\n分かっていますけど……\nにゃは……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20046,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2004601,
            "DisplayOrder": 580,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8780,
            "LocalizeKR": "그게 저~ 네~ 네~\n송구합니다…….",
            "LocalizeJP": "ええと……はい……\n申し訳ありません。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20046,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2004601,
            "DisplayOrder": 590,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 15050,
            "LocalizeKR": "그렇지만~ 뭐라고 할까~\n저희 쪽에도 내부 사정이란 게\n있어서~",
            "LocalizeJP": "でもほら、\nなんといいますかぁ〜\nこちらにも事情という\nものがありましてねぇ～？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20046,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2004601,
            "DisplayOrder": 600,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 3780,
            "LocalizeKR": "냐핫?! 아뇨, 아뇨!",
            "LocalizeJP": "にゃはっ！？いえいえ！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20046,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2004601,
            "DisplayOrder": 610,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11720,
            "LocalizeKR": "당치도 않습니다!\n반성하고 있습니다!\n예! 예!",
            "LocalizeJP": "滅相もない！\n反省していますとも！ええ！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
